Entries (Players / Teams)
In Tournament.app, "Entries" refer to Players or Teams participating in a tournament.

GET
/tournaments/:id/entries
https://api.tournament.io/v1/public/tournaments/:id/entries
This endpoint retrieves all entries for a specific tournament. Whether they are individual players or teams, depends on each disciplines entry type.

